==Estonian==
'''-ta'''

# suffix for the [[abessive case]], [[without]].

====Usage====
*Suffixed to the [[genitive]] singular.
*Often used in conjunction with the preposition [[ilma]], for example ''ilma soolata'' "without salt, saltless".

