==Finnish==

===Case suffix===
'''-ta''' ''(in words with back vowel harmony)''

'''-tä''' ''(in words with front vowel harmony)''

# a suffix for the [[partitive]] case.

====Usage====
*This suffix is used after a long vowel, diphthong or a consonant.

